headline: ICE Launches Average Prime Offer Rates (APOR) Index
summary: ATLANTA & NEW YORK, June 17, 2025--Intercontinental Exchange, Inc. (NYSE: ICE), a leading global provider of technology and data, today announced the launch of the ICE Average Prime Offer Rates Index (ICE APOR), which is updated weekly on the ICE Index Platform and publicly available.
